{"id": "1470736167489110087", "channel_id": "1436913827571695898", "type": 19, "author_id": "1372028651175936080", "author_name": "Morimens", "author_bot": true, "content": "**2nd Anniversary Event – Quick Take**\n\n- **Rewards:** Up to 200 × *Luminous Core* (limited pulls) + a selectable SSR Awakener for using the Posse skill 200 times.  \n- **Tasks:** Log‑ins, main‑story clears, and Posse‑skill usage are the only requirements – pretty straightforward.  \n- **Generosity:** Compared to previous events, the pull cap is high and the SSR Awakener is guaranteed, so the event is **quite generous** for both free‑to‑play and paying players.  \n\n**Bottom line:** The event is solid – lots of pull currency and a guaranteed SSR make it worth grinding the simple tasks.  \n\n*(No emotional fluff, just the facts.)*", "timestamp": "2026-02-10T11:00:27.286000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["694573382380945529"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1470736143405289641", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
